---
// Callout - static bold statement
---

<section class="callout-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="circle-deco" style="width:400px;height:400px;top:-20%;left:-5%;"></div>
    <p class="callout-text reveal">
      We bridge the gap between <span class="callout-highlight">comic shops with overstock</span> and <span class="callout-highlight">readers who want great books</span> — bringing consignment titles and indie releases to communities across Middle Tennessee.
    </p>
    <div class="spin-plus reveal" style="font-size:2.5rem;">+</div>
  </div>
</section>
